WEBVTT

00:00.150 --> 00:02.640
Lain, what do you want?

00:03.100 --> 00:04.160
Pleasure?

00:04.160 --> 00:05.330
Excitement?

00:05.700 --> 00:06.700
Friends?

00:07.180 --> 00:08.080
Me?

00:08.900 --> 00:13.080
What I need right now is someone who wants to know me.

00:13.880 --> 00:16.460
Touko-san promised me.

00:16.960 --> 00:18.720
She said that she would understand me.

00:19.590 --> 00:21.360
She said that she would choose me.
